Class Summary

PendingIn This class maintains a list of pending service requests, kept by a component making the service requests.
PendingOut This class maintains a list of pending service requests, kept by the service handling the requests.
ServiceDescription This class implements a service description object.
ServiceDescriptions This class maintains a list of service descriptions.
ServiceInput This class implements a service input object used for executing a service.
